high_descs: Walk forward to the stove top, then turn left and walk forward across the room to the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the lettuce from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn right and walk slightly forward, then turn left towards the counter.
Put the lettuce on the counter, in front of the large knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned head of lettuce on a counter top.

high_descs: Go forward to the stove, hang a left, go across the room to the counter where the lettuce is.
Pick up the lettuce that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go forward to the sink that is on the right.
Put the lettuce in the sink, rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn to the right, go back to the counter on the left where the plant is.
Put the lettuce on the counter in front of the yellow handled knife.
anns.task_desc: Put clean lettuce on a counter.

high_descs: Walk forward to the stove then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's in front of you.
Move to your left until you're close enough to use the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Take a step to your right.
Put the lettuce on the counter below the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on the sink.
